This is an application which enables taking-notes about our mistakes during learning or working as well as tracking easily. It is called Mistake Tracker

Main Features:
- Write (Can Edit): 
  + We can create any categories that we want.
  + Depending on our mistakes, we may set its level from 1 to 10.
  + To add our mistake on Application, we need Fill in three types of information, including: Name, Wrong Description, Cause, and Solution.
- Read (Can Edit):
  + You can find our mistakes through search tool, categories, and level.
  + Our mistakes has two modes that is brief and detail.
    + brief consists of ID, Name, Date, Wrong Description, Cause, Solution, Level, and Status of improving(Not Started, In Progress, Done).
    + Detail is that same what you write.
